data.description: Please view the 3D tour.  Like "Brand New" Home!** Come check out this gorgeous 3 bath/3 bedroom (plus den/office) home with 2 en-suites!!! The beautiful double entry doors with transom window allow for plenty of natural Florida sunlight making this home seem even more open! This property is luxury at its finest (located in the heart of North Port) with porcelain wood plank tile, granite countertops, solid wood cabinets, 9'4" high tray ceilings with crown molding, 5 1/4" baseboards, all stainless appliances, nesting sliders to lanai, and also has hurricane impact windows. The master bedroom boasts an expansive custom-made walk-in closet to get you organized. The stunning master bath has granite counters and the tiled walk-in shower makes this luxurious home even more amazing for the price! The 2 master suites at opposite ends of home make it perfect for your guests/family's privacy and comfort. This home has a vacant lot next to it and also behind it for added privacy! There is plenty of room for a pool in the backyard also.
